qas.question: Which company took over the channels vacated by Saint FM?
What date did Saint FM Community Radio launch?
What kind of people can join Saint Fm Radio Community?

context: <a0_0>Saint FM Community Radio<a0_0/> took over the radio channels vacated by Saint FM and launched on <a1_0>10 March 2013<a1_0/>. The station operates as a limited-by-guarantee company owned by its members and is registered as a fund-raising Association. Membership is open to <a2_0>everyone<a2_0/>, and grants access to a live audio stream.
